{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 74.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I'm about a half a block away from my house running, this SS man screams, halt, stop.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I raised my hands right away and he has this gun and he says, do you know what time it is?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I says, I live right here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you know what time it is?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He slapped me a couple of times, he kicked me, and he let me go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the days before, the days after I could hear one time right behind our windows-- we lived on the second floor-- behind our windows I could hear one was shot right in front of the window.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I could hear his-- his dying-- his dying sounds and how depressing, how tragic, how frightened we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were just squeezing ourselves one to another and we just couldn't believe that this is happening to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We worked every day, we came home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Food was scarce, everything was rationed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You had to get your bread by coupons and the coupons you got through the working card and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a big black market, naturally, and people sold their whatever, their possessions they had to feed themselves and other things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yet the Jewish Council, on the Jewish committee, the Jewish gemeide-- gemeide is a German word, G-E-M-E-I-D-E-- the Jewish gemeide, Yiddish gemeide, they tried to organize schools, they tried to make life a little bit more bearable.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But of course, it was all under the auspices of the German government and they-- whatever the Jewish gemeide tried to do, they just knocked it down.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the main problemm-- the main function of this Jewish gemede was to deliver the Jewish people to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
